          people have reliable access to safe drinking water. With a growing
          population, high levels of poverty, and plagued by natural disasters,
          Pakistan is facing a water crisis.
        </p>
        <p
          class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
        >
          Children and the elderly are the most at risk from water-borne illness
          and poor sanitation. Almost half of deaths in the country are related
          to the contaminated water supply. At Al-Wahab Foundation, our priority
          is to ensure that underprivileged communities have access to clean
          drinking water to protect and save their lives. From sustainable and <span
            class="font-bold">well-maintained water pumps to water wells</span
          >, your donation can help us achieve our goal. Donate water pump in
          Pakistan and help those in need.
        </p>
      </div>

