          Water Crisis in Uganda
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-2 text-grey text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-justify"
        >
          Africa faces a severe water crisis, with a significant portion of its
          population lacking access to clean and safe water sources. The
          scarcity of clean water poses a significant threat to public health
          and exacerbates the vulnerability of communities, particularly women
          and children, to waterborne diseases. In response to this situation
          specifically <a
            href="#"
            class="font-bold text-maroon hover:text-customBeige"
